# Dispatching Parallel Agents

Full instructions: `.agents/skills/dispatching-parallel-agents/SKILL.md`.

- **Trigger**: Auto — consider when you see 3+ independent subtasks
- **Key rule**: Only parallelize low-coupling work. High-coupling = sequential.
- **Do NOT use**: For tasks under 3 files, or when subtasks share state
